---
import SectionHeader from "../SectionHeader.astro";
import CTAButton from "../CTAButton.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative bg-depth py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden"
  aria-labelledby="join-title"
>
  <!-- Atmospheric radial gradient dome - Deep Lemurian Glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_center,_rgba(255,215,0,0.1)_0%,_rgba(156,39,176,0.1)_40%,_transparent_70%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-[1] max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="reveal">
      <SectionHeader
        label="Walk With Me"
        title="Some paths are meant to be walked together"
        id="join-title"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="reveal space-y-6">
      <p>
        On select pilgrimages, a small number of souls will be invited to walk
        alongside me. To stand on the sacred ground. To participate in ceremony.
        To feel the earth beneath your feet, not through a screen.
      </p>

      <p>
        These are intimate gatherings â€” limited by intention, not by numbers.
      </p>

      <p>
        If this calls to you, subscribing is the first step. All in-person
        journey invitations are shared inside the circle first.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal mt-12">
      <div class="image-treated">
        <img
          src="/helena-leading-spiritual-group-walk-egypt-temple.jpeg"
          alt="Helena leading a spiritual group walk at an Egyptian temple"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="w-full h-auto block rounded-lg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton
        href="https://www.instagram.com/"
        text="Subscribe on Instagram"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
